@startuml
actor User
participant "Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Route Handler\nPOST /api/recommendation-chat/messages" as Route
participant "Supabase Auth" as Auth
participant "Recommendation Chat Service" as Service
participant "OpenAI API" as OpenAI
participant "Chat Repository" as Repository
database "Supabase DB\nchat, movies, tags" as Database

User -> Frontend: 추천 질문 입력
Frontend -> Route: POST /api/recommendation-chat/messages
Route -> Auth: 현재 세션 확인
Auth --> Route: userId 반환
Route -> Service: 추천 채팅 메시지 처리
Service -> Repository: conversation 조회 또는 생성
Repository -> Database: conversation select/insert
Service -> OpenAI: 추천 의도 분석 요청
OpenAI --> Service: 분석 결과
Service -> Repository: 추천 후보 조회
Repository -> Database: tags, similarities, movies 조회
Database --> Repository: candidate movies
Service -> OpenAI: 추천 사유 생성 요청
OpenAI --> Service: 추천 사유
Service -> Repository: 메시지와 추천 영화 저장
Repository -> Database: messages, message_movies insert
Repository --> Service: 저장 결과
Service --> Route: 추천 채팅 응답
Route --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: 추천 응답 표시
@enduml
